type: tab-list
title: API Reference

- Overview
  REST API built on HTTP with JSON payloads.
  Base URL: https://api.example.com/v1
- Authentication
  Use Bearer tokens in the Authorization header.
  Tokens expire after 24 hours.
- Rate Limits
  100 requests per minute per API key.
  Burst up to 200 req/s for 10 seconds.
